{"tid":423463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼：踢波怕傷不如去捉棋","createTime":"2017-10-04T02:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:13:26.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"496549f2e80fc9646cd3782d46923060fec94a1c","tid":423463,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"堅尼：踢波怕傷不如去捉棋<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=eXP4m7GrBESckn%2BuOuspJxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=846527cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前曼聯隊長堅尼球員時代打甩門牙帶血吞，日前戲謔：「如果怕受傷、怕被撞，不如咪踢波，捉棋好過。」<br />\n<br />\n美式足球研究報告證實，頭部經常遇到衝擊，的確會造成腦震盪，而愛爾蘭前鋒奇雲杜里上周就因腦震盪，毅然決定掛靴。「我認為需要更多研究，但如果你是擔心體育運動的碰撞，不如捉棋吧！」愛爾蘭國家隊助教堅尼（Roy Keane）表示：「碰撞是足球運動的一部份，美式足球、欖球亦然，所有運動都有風險。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到34歲老將奇雲杜里的情況，堅尼回應道：「他可能被腦震盪幾年，感覺不妥，顯然地，退休是正確的決定。但是，所有人都明白碰撞是比賽的一部份，他是前鋒，無可避免會與中堅正面對撼，我會祝福他。」<br />\n<br />\n世界盃歐洲區外圍賽D組，愛爾蘭以13分守住第3位，分別落後威爾斯和塞爾維亞1分和5分，綠軍將於周五主場對摩爾多瓦。"},{"pid":"c219d5a8dfb87aa3a4e158cd0f6744773cc5fdf0","tid":423463,"uid":53543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"@皮鞋"},{"pid":"f1851e6edf468b17a9f8218b2ca1390bcbd24cdd","tid":423463,"uid":19962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140702/large/02s4-011p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140702%2Flarge%2F02s4-011p.jpg&h=810c263a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f2e850ee62fe3a0ecc71f6f335d8cd3a09ecf94","tid":423463,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140702/large/02s4-011p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140702%2Flarge%2F02s4-011p.jpg&h=810c263a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚比人踢就坐輪椅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7a9724c20b10d63fd30caa1e01024a519e5c8a","tid":423463,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"打冰壺啦"},{"pid":"c624752b6784686970cffec54b723c32957fc24e","tid":423463,"uid":40588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/133130_9a8d00148ba8a289c916f8109707d16b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F133130_9a8d00148ba8a289c916f8109707d16b.jpg&h=5c4b4dc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7524ab4b912dee84c4f95039814c5441909c3992","tid":423463,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"腦震盪 腦震盪 腦震盪~<br />\n皮鞋道理~"},{"pid":"95387952ebae05fe876cdb6b99992964433e04f1","tid":423463,"uid":134462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dc6900654b429fd0369a5e341dfb3759ad5142d","tid":423463,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"堅尼果啲矛招唔係要你傷, 係要收你皮"},{"pid":"43255ccdbdfd599166be7a24920b6181c4e64a0b","tid":423463,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腦震盪 腦震盪 腦震盪~<br />\n皮鞋道理~</blockquote><br />\n歌神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf8d68922bba598b52e41a90f9aead377ecfa81","tid":423463,"uid":15793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"捉棋先危險<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/181153_02d27e3bfeb76cf39760afb43c7f309e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%